headline: TD Cowen Highlights Steady Execution at Union Pacific (UNP) After Q4 Results
summary: Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE:UNP) is included among the 12 Best Stocks to Buy for the Long Term. On January 28, TD Cowen trimmed its price target on Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE:UNP) to $255 from $257 while maintaining a Buy rating. The firm updated its outlook after the company reported Q4 results that reflected steady execution, […]
